NOTES FROM THE EDITOR

It’s been a little over a month since we launched Redistribute Megazine, and we’ve been absolutely thrilled with the response we’ve received. So many of you have messaged and emailed us, or shared articles you’ve enjoyed reading, and we’ve loved seeing every one of them.

text: NOTES FROM THE EDITOR

It’s been a little over a month since we launched Redistribute Megazine, and we’ve been absolutely thrilled with the response we’ve received. So many of you have messaged and emailed us, or shared articles you’ve enjoyed reading, and we’ve loved seeing every one of them.

items.text: Popular Reviews
In our first month we’ve published reviews of some great new music by artists such as Apanorama, Janus Rasmussen, and Shibui Nigai. ﻿
There’s many more online now. Enjoy reading.
